title: Online Tournament - Master/Challenger Team Dominant

embed.description: Welcome to PacificPeninsula.net! We are proud to announce our website is finally up & running. Keep an eye out for tournaments and events! In the near future, we will have a tournament system for you all to sign-up and play with ease! | TOURNAMENT: 20th of December - A December to Remember!

body:
Dear Summoners,

This tournament has had 4 extremely high elo teams sign-up. If anyone wishes to sign-up for a good battle and practice, or a chance to meet new people, then sign-up!

1st place prize: 1k RP each, Triumphant Ryze + Ryze, BONUS PRIZE: MVP of team receieves Arctic Ops Varus + Varus
All other places from 2-8 receive a 4 Win IP boost!

Cheers
